name: DJ Paypal
description: '''DJ Paypal''' is a [[footwork (Chicago)|footwork]] producer. Born in [[North Carolina]], they reside in [[Berlin]] and are a member of the Teklife crew. They have often performed live with their face hidden for reasons of anonymity. Their 2015 debut album, ''[[Sold Out (DJ Paypal album)|Sold Out]]'', was released on [[Brainfeeder]] to generally favorable reviews.
